Package: wickracopilot
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Market-Context Copilot Core
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-copilot over its C ABI hub: build a Copilot
    from a spec JSON, drive it with command JSON and read back a ranked list of
    hard facts - the same protocol as the CLI and every other binding. Only the
    deterministic core is exposed; the LLM adapter is never reachable over the C
    ABI.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-copilot
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-copilot/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-copilot C ABI shared library (WKCOPILOT_LIB) and
    its header (WKCOPILOT_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
